========================================================
TIER 3 — NEUTRAL ENVIRONMENT
========================================================

Characteristics:

• Mixed signals
• Moderate continuation
• Increased noise
• Rotational behavior
• Balanced flows

Implications:

Reduce conviction

Reduce:

• trade frequency
• position size
• continuation assumptions

========================================================
TIER 4 — FRAGILE ENVIRONMENT
========================================================

Characteristics:

• Frequent liquidity sweeps
• Compression
• Weak persistence
